ON=WEAVE
	sayu No, this is my natural hair.  Why do you ask?
ON=WOOL
	sayu Sheep are such filthy animals, but wool makes wonderful tunics.
ON=YARN
	sayu Oh, I make things with yarn all the time.
ON=GUILD
ON=JOIN
	sayu I recommend you develop a sense of color first.
ON=MASTER
	sayu I'm am a master of cloth, color, and all things frilly.

